snippet.title: ARC Raiders | Reveal & Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
ARC Raiders is a free-to-play, third-person, PvPvE extraction shooter. Sign up for playtesting on Steam.

Wishlist on Epic & Steam now.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1808500/
Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/p/arc-raiders
